REBO2(+S) LAMMPS MODULE
=======================

Installation instructions.

Run in the (current) source directory:

make copy
make

This should create a librebo2.a. Now copy pair_rebo2.cpp and pair_rebo2.h
to the LAMMPS src directory. Modify the LAMMPS Makefile to link to librebo2.a,
some LAPACK library and the fortran runtime (-lifcore -lifport for ifort,
-lgfortran for gfortran).

